N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4118.7 - Incomplete finish

State Regulations

If there is any premium for which no horse has maintained
a position either through failure to start or to finish or through
disqualification, such premium shall go to the race winner. Notes
